perf: optimize FeloService pro list read file process
- Refactor `check_is_pro` to use buffered reading of `felo_search_pro.txt` instead of loading the entire file into memory - Add trimming and empty check for email string in `check_is_pro` - Replace `get_pro_list` with more efficient line-by-line reading implementation - Add new helper method `get_pro_bufreader_lines` to read lines from `felo_search_pro.txt` with buffered reader - Introduce `parse_pro_to_email` helper function for parsing lines to `Email` - Import `tokio::fs` in test module for setting up tests

feat: enhance Email Binding Validation and Add Pro User Checks
- Modify `validate_user` function to check if a user is already bound using `get_binding_by_userid` and handle different scenarios for email and Felo Search Pro status. - Add checks for updating bindings for Felo Search Pro users within one month. - Update tests for `validate_user` to include scenarios for checking bindings by user ID and email. - Add new test cases for `validate_user` to handle pro users trying to change email within one month. - Refactor `FeloService` to use `BufReader` and `Lines` for reading bindings. - Add `get_binding_by_userid` and refactor `get_binding_by_email` in `FeloService`. - Modify `get_bindings` to use a helper function for setting up test data. - Add new tests for `get_binding_by_userid` and `get_binding_by_email` in `FeloService`.
Signed-off-by: 陳鈞 Jim <jim@miniasp.com>

feat: refactor Felo feature for better testing and logging
- Add tests for `step_bind_history` and `validate_user` functions - Refactor `felosearchpro` command to use `step_bind_history` and `validate_user` - Add `write_audit_log` function to `FeloService` for logging actions - Add audit logging in `adjust_discord_role` and `add_pro_role` functions - Improve error messages and logging in `FeloHandler` - Refactor imports and module attributes for better organization - Improve documentation for `FeloService` methods - Fix handling of invalid email format in `validate_user` - Mock `FeloService` in tests for `validate_user` function - Add tests for edge cases in `step_bind_history` and `validate_user` functions
Signed-off-by: 陳鈞 Jim <jim@miniasp.com>

refactor: streamline User Timeout with Helper Function
- Add `timeout_user` utility function to handle user timeouts - Replace inline timeout logic with `timeout_user` function in `felosearchpro` command - Replace inline timeout logic with `timeout_user` function in `join` command - Import `timeout_user` in relevant files - Add `timeout_user` module to `util.rs`
Signed-off-by: 陳鈞 Jim <jim@miniasp.com>

refactor: refactor FeloService with Constants for File Paths
